 LL salute to agents: "My agent spent six years in therapy getting in touch 
with his inner child. Now he's in a 12-step program for adults who wet the 
bed." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Rowland Kerr 
</P>
<P>
 "Nancy Kerrigan's agent has left his wife and is now dating Nancy. But he 
still won't return her phone calls." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Paul Ryan 
</P>
