</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Spanish-Language Parents' Magazine: Children's Television Workshop will begin 
publishing a Spanish-language version of its Sesame Street Parents magazine in 
February. The quarterly Padres de Sesame Street will focus on the care of 
infants, toddlers and children ages 6 to 11 and on issues of health, safety and 
education. It will be distributed through physicians in areas with significant 
Latino populations. 
</P>
