<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA111194-0220 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 097587 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 11, 1994, Friday, Valley Edition 
</P>
