COMMUNITY NEWS FOCUS: HOLIDAY CLOSINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Today is Veterans Day. The following schedule is in effect: 
</P>
<P>
 * Federal, county and most city offices are closed.Irvine City Hall also will 
be closed Monday. The city halls of Brea, Laguna Hills, Los Alamitos and 
Westminster are open.  
</P>
<P>
 * County, state and federal courthouses are closed. 
</P>
<P>
 * City and county libraries are closed.  
</P>
<P>
 * Banks are closed.  
</P>
<P>
 * Schools, colleges and universities are closed. Fullerton K-6 also will be 
closed Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 * Mail: There is no postal delivery.  
</P>
<P>
 * Trash: Trash is collected as regularly scheduled. 
</P>
<P>
 * Buses: OCTA buses run on regular schedule.  
</P>
<P>
 * Parks: All city- and county-run parks are open. 
</P>
