COMMUNITY NEWS FOCUS: NEWPORT BEACH; HOTEL WINS AWARD FOR ENERGY EFFICIENCY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By HOLLY J. WAGNER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Le Meridien Hotel has received an energy efficiency award from Southern 
California Edison Co. for installing energy efficiency equipment and adopting 
practices that will reduce energy consumption and save the hotel up to $50,000 
a year. 
</P>
<P>
 The measures include variable-speed drive controls on air conditioners and 
water pumps and controls that reduce air conditioning and use outdoor air when 
the weather cools. HOLLY J. WAGNER 
