<HEADLINE>
<P>
CITY SECTION FOOTBALL ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JOE SCHLOSSER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 In other Valley Pac-8 Conference games: 
</P>
<P>
 North Hollywood 46, Poly 31 -- Dante Clay gained 263 yards in 21 carries and 
scored on runs of 68, one and 19 yards to lead the Huskies (3-7, 3-4) at North 
Hollywood. 
</P>
<P>
 Teammate Ryan Jones caught four passes for 154 yards and three touchdowns. 
</P>
<P>
 Bruce Gage intercepted three passes and scored on an 89-yard kickoff return to 
break open a close game early in the second half. 
</P>
<P>
 Quarterback Ricardo Gamboa of Poly (2-8, 2-5) completed 19 of 35 passes for 
359 yards and four touchdowns. He also threw four interceptions. Gamboa added 
three two-point conversion passes. Receiver Paul Cespedes caught touchdown 
passes of 25 and 52 yards. 
</P>
<P>
 North Hollywood quarterback Jesus Acosta completed four of six passes, all to 
Jones, for 154 yards and three touchdowns with two interceptions. JOE SCHLOSSER 
</P>
