<P>
 Contract dispute -- Ericsson GE has filed a claim with the county protesting 
the bidding process for a countywide communication system. Stories Nov. 3 and 4 
incorrectly said the claim was filed by a firm that was Ericsson's partner in 
the bidding. 
</P>
