<P>
 Wrong caption -- A photo caption Saturday incorrectly identified two officials 
at the Lincoln Neighborhood Park opening in Simi Valley. The officials cutting 
the ribbon were Bonnie Carpenter and Don Funk, both members of the Rancho Simi 
Recreation and Park District board. 
