<TEXT>
<P>
 Wrong numbers -- A list of election returns Thursday incorrectly reported some 
of the results for Measure C in Port Hueneme. Final unofficial returns showed 
1,365 voters wanted to adopt a flat-rate assessment and 610 residents wanted to 
follow recommendations made by a study committee. 
</P>
